#phrase Rick  1
When the world was whole, Gipath was just a small corner of a vast continent. After the Joons' power vanished, other states appeared here...
#CAMERA 11
#ANIMATION 5
#phrase Rick  2
The Night of Troubles which splintered the world destroyed those states. There are even fewer traces of them than there are of the long-forgotten Joons. Only two Empires managed to survive the Night of Troubles, the two eternal rivals - Cania and Khadagan.
#CAMERA 7
#ANIMATION 6
#phrase Rick  3
Cania, whither you will soon go, seems to me to be a country where the rulers are not especially cruel and the subjects feel relatively free. Do not succumb to the temptation to relax, always use caution there!
